{"tid":21119,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本遊戲最後希望FF15同Witcher3比如何?","createTime":"2016-12-03T16:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T17:52:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67ec65d4f7f6cf6cbad1b5d68a0ef8cee73f01d9","tid":21119,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"呢到會有d現FFXV玩通頂既人同你講佢玩巫師玩左半個鐘就棄game <br />\n亦有人會講巫師3主線悶但對於歐美同日本對於XV主線又短又無聊到反晒艇一事隻字不提 <br />\nFFXIII拆成三部曲時高大家鬧到咩咁但而家又有一堆人期待XV出續作（但其實製作人已經講死左今作一部完而且DLC唔會影響主線）"},{"pid":"8b9bbd82668e71b62e0dab0cc2af4c6f8acd04d5","tid":21119,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"冇玩FF但肯定Witcher好玩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107da04c190b84a2a1b480411eb32ada9a56c826","tid":21119,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可以排好啲版同執執佢先<br />\n可能我中文差睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ed59d179b18d478c6a297a0eaa9cd02067876d","tid":21119,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"玩過巫師2+3，FF零式,1,3,4,7,10,12,13,FF15暫時玩左8個鐘。<br />\n感覺上FF15前期主線太廢，衰過FF13，只係戰鬥上面比較有趣。<br />\n而巫師由頭到尾劇情都算緊湊，就算有支線任都有好多細節。<br />\n例如FF15討伐任務悶到死，接完ORDER就打怪收工，<br />\n前期得煙灰眼叫做有啲野睇，<br />\n但係巫師每接一個討伐任務都會去了解發生左咩事。<br />\n重有FF15啲嘴型奇奇怪怪，連CG同劇情版都唔係好岩嘴型。"},{"pid":"c2197e722e62dc9eaf7540a35d7351c2fadc6bcb","tid":21119,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"戰鬥明顯ffxv高質啲<br />\n但係支線任巫師完勝"},{"pid":"724a70e05be885e8b312eae9c47f899a4f6176a8","tid":21119,"uid":1979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戰鬥明顯ffxv高質啲<br />\n但係支線任巫師完勝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗巫師既戰鬥好多game都完勝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0869605b06497fbac32c490362a21810609198d0","tid":21119,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"兩隻GAME性質完全唔同冇得比"},{"pid":"df13841512dfaa3243f3efd8f322d6caf86116dc","tid":21119,"uid":4203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:33:03.000Z","msg":"巫師除左戰鬥系統同物品介面廢之外<br />\n我諗唔到其他缺點<br />\n<br />\n主線支線一樣精彩<br />\n血腥男爵兩種結局令人深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係花園追 特莉絲個場愛情戲 可以選擇咀唔咀佢<br />\n咀就可以扑 但要背叛葉奈法 令人內心掙扎<br />\n守城戰CG 媲美電影水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三巫婆既身材樣貌同 蔣麗芸 梁美芬 葛博士差唔多<br />\n前段至後段既選擇都會影響結局 <br />\nDLC份量是前所未見<br />\n<br />\n得罪個句<br />\n暫時得The Last of us劇情比得上巫師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而開放式世界同劇情之間既平衡 <br />\n巫師絕對完勝FF15<br />\n<br />\nFF15既劇情真心有問題<br />\n好似一部被腰斬既漫畫咁 畫畫下 跳左去十年後<br />\n佢個支線都係勁無聊 幫人打怪影相 冇轉折位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係戰鬥好過巫師 好似玩緊MH咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b060675dc144c0c5a4dbe03fd4c7c5c7d629c6d","tid":21119,"uid":14704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"巫師玩左一個星期 <br />\n淨係支線都覺得好有心絲<br />\n每個任都有內容<br />\n唔似其他game咁 尻打怪就算👍🏻"},{"pid":"e5a4fb87ec5cc50f57f28163180279cbd54ae0bf","tid":21119,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本遊戲最後希望一定係From Software<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa3732389fe5c8f26cb472b2b97a25cd334d92a","tid":21119,"uid":15917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巫師除左戰鬥系統同物品介面廢之外<br />\n我諗唔到其他缺點<br />\n<br />\n主線支線一樣精彩<br />\n血腥男爵兩種結局令人深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係花園追 特莉絲個場愛情戲 可以選擇咀唔咀佢<br />\n咀就可以扑 但要背叛葉奈法 令人內心掙扎<br />\n守城戰CG 媲美電影水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三巫婆既身材樣貌同 蔣麗芸 梁美芬 葛博士差唔多<br />\n前段至後段既選擇都會影響結局 <br />\nDLC份量是前所未見<br />\n<br />\n得罪個句<br />\n暫時得The Last of us劇情比得上巫師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而開放式世界同劇情之間既平衡 <br />\n巫師絕對完勝FF15<br />\n<br />\nFF15既劇情真心有問題<br />\n好似一部被腰斬既漫畫咁 畫畫下 跳左去十年後<br />\n佢個支線都係勁無聊 幫人打怪影相 冇轉折位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係戰鬥好過巫師 好似玩緊MH咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你我咀撚左都冇得扑"},{"pid":"c67c5d3a4526eabbb2cea287a3f320a55bbfa60d","tid":21119,"uid":39840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"唔需要比黎比去,<br />\n兩隻GAME一齊玩晒佢"},{"pid":"8d95849fc609be4fa6fbcb1e5312d1c99117523c","tid":21119,"uid":23964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔需要比黎比去,<br />\n兩隻GAME一齊玩晒佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c045456bc0f92c20a66499e32b886545a4b87b4","tid":21119,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"講劇情無得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地有曬成個世界觀<br />\n仲要專登係有咁細節得咁細<br />\n3集都有關聯<br />\n<br />\nff 15 剩係整隻game都佔大部分時間<br />\n仲邊到有咁多時間諗世界觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該過多幾年先再慢慢加d野落去<br />\n<br />\n玩落就知勁縮水<br />\n一開始話個地圖係gta5 既5倍<br />\n後來變左係成個大陸(大部分無係隻game到)係gta5 既5倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f5f1d00b4f39a923e2738ca0ea2d651be6e195","tid":21119,"uid":1135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"巫師3集先完曬成個故事 個世界設定 人物角色補完同增強左咁多次 FF點比 <br />\nFF集集都獨新故事 (除左x-2 月之歸還 7cc個堆後/前傳）<br />\nFF唯一可取就係相對爽快既戰鬥同咁多年黎既某d傳統野翻新左 令到老玩家都buy佢 e.g陸利鳥 飛空艇（車） 合體技<br />\nFF玩落個氣氛就叫有笑有淚 前期輕鬆 後期開始有番咁上下劇情轉折 但就好快ending <br />\n巫師就成隻game個氣氛都形造得幾凝重 戰爭期間 又要救個囡 又要防止世界末日 d村又成日俾人屠殺<br />\n亂世feel<br />\nBtw 2隻我都覺得好玩 但FF就未做到100分囉 開發左十年都係得咁少野玩<br />\n巫師 唔洗我講啦 玩過都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8c688d3b362bd91fc0329f647ebf4616fbf6d5","tid":21119,"uid":43001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"Witcher <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1470946340c5c550a14783051cdda746cffddf28","tid":21119,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"一下子就打大佬？同隻goty比咁高攀呀<br />\n同watch dog/mafia/fallout比贏先囉"}]}